    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you gain the ability to surround yourself in fire as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Swift-Actions\">swift action</a>. This fire burns for a number of rounds per day equal to your character level plus your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;bonus. These rounds do not have to be consecutive.</p>\n<p>Any unarmed attacks you make while affected by immolation deal an additional 1d6 points of fire damage, and any creature that ends its turn adjacent to you while youâ€™re affected by immolation also takes 1d6 points of fire damage.</p>",
